@3SAEstate showcasing the Marbella lifestyle at Casa Mimosa! 🌴☀️ This villa is characterized by an elegant living space with modern clean lines and plenty of glass providing natural light and seamless integration of indoor and outdoor living. The property is everything you need to experience the best of the Mediterranean lifestyle, distributed on three levels. 😍

Property details:
✔️ Surface 517 M²⁠⠀⁠
✔️ Plot 1258 M²⠀
✔️ Terrace 320 M²
✔️ ⁠5 Bedrooms⁠⠀
✔️ Large roof terrace
✔️ Swimming pool
✔️ Outdoor gym
✔️ Jacuzzi

Contact @3SAEstate for more information ✨
-

#realestate #marbella #marbellarealestate #luxurylifestyle #marbellavilla #marbellamansion #luxuryrealestate #listing #marbellalifestyle #marbellaspain #summer #houses

node.text:
@Empire_Realty_Group_ with a new exclusive listing in Vaughan Ontario ✨🔑

Welcome to This Exquisite Custom Crafted Home Featuring Unsurpassed Craftsmanship. Enter Through Elegant Grand Gates to be Surrounded w/ Lavish Landscaping, Gorgeous Greenery & A Breathtaking Backyard Oasis. Boasts Approximately 6000 sqft of Living Space. Sitting on a Premium 100x150 ft Lot, Nestled In One Of The Most Prestigious Pockets Of Maple, Vaughan, Ontario. This Home Will Impress The Pickiest Buyer. This One Of A Kind 4+2 Bedroom Bungaloft Offers Fully Finished Walk-Up Basement Suitable for Duel Families, In-Laws, or Nannies Quarters. Conveniently Located Just Steps to Schools, Trails, Plaza, Groceries, Cafes & Minutes to Major Highways, Cortelucci Vaughan Hospital, Wonderland, Vaughan Mills Mall & More! 

👉🏼 @empire_realty_group_
